# Pinned sha256 of CachyOS's cachyos-repo.tar.xz (the bootstrap that modules/00-base.sh
# runs AS ROOT). modules/00-base.sh is FAIL-CLOSED: with no pin here and no override it
# refuses to run the tarball.
#
# To pin (do this once, from a TRUSTED machine):
#   1. curl -fLO https://mirror.cachyos.org/cachyos-repo.tar.xz
#   2. verify it against CachyOS's published checksum / your own trust path
#   3. sha256sum cachyos-repo.tar.xz   ->   put the 64-hex digest on its own line below
#
# Until a digest is committed below, install with ONE of:
#   ARCHFRICAN_CACHYOS_SHA256=<digest> ...        (pin for one run)
#   ARCHFRICAN_ALLOW_UNVERIFIED_CACHYOS=1 ...      (explicitly accept the risk)
#
# A line that is exactly 64 lowercase hex chars is read as the pin; everything else is ignored.
#
# <paste the 64-hex sha256 here>
